ZH: 我用筛子过滤了咖啡渣。
EN: I filtered the coffee grounds with a sieve.

ZH: 她用筛子将面粉过筛。
EN: She sifted the flour with a sieve.

ZH: 筛子可以将杂质分离出来。
EN: A sieve can separate impurities.

ZH: 这个筛子有很多小孔。
EN: This sieve has many small holes.

ZH: 奶奶用筛子过滤了豆浆。
EN: Grandma filtered the soy milk with a sieve.

ZH: 她用筛子将蜂蜜过滤去渣。
EN: She used a sieve to filter out impurities from the honey.

ZH: 筛子能将水从固体中过滤出来。
EN: The sieve can filter water from solids.

ZH: 他用筛子将沙子过滤。
EN: He sifted the sand with a sieve.

ZH: 这个筛子的孔太大，过滤不了细小颗粒。
EN: The holes in this sieve are too big to filter fine particles.

ZH: 妈妈用筛子把面筛得很细。
EN: Mom sieved the flour finely with a sieve.

ZH: 我们用筛子过滤了饭粒和水。
EN: We filtered out rice grains and water with a sieve.

ZH: 他把红枣和枸杞放入一个筛子里洗净。
EN: He washed the jujubes and wolfberries in a sieve.

ZH: 厨师用筛子过滤了汤里的渣滓。
EN: The chef sieved the residue from the soup with a sieve.

ZH: 孩子们用筛子在沙堆中玩耍。
EN: The children played with sieves in the sandpit.

ZH: 筛子的用途很广泛，不仅仅用于厨房。
EN: Sieves have a wide range of applications, not only in the kitchen.

ZH: 这个筛子的质量很好，不容易生锈。
EN: This sieve has good quality and is not easily rusted.

ZH: 我用筛子将墙上的灰尘过滤去除。
EN: I used a sieve to filter out the dust on the wall.

ZH: 这个筛子的设计很巧妙，滤网不易变形。
EN: The design of this sieve is clever, and the mesh is not easily deformed.

ZH: 她学会了使用筛子过滤茶叶中的杂质。
EN: She learned to use a sieve to filter impurities from tea leaves.

ZH: 筛子的形状和大小可以根据需要进行选择。
EN: The shape and size of the sieve can be chosen according to needs.
